headline: The Ultimate Healthcare Robotics Stock to Buy With $600 Right Now
summary: What is the da Vinci surgical robot?  As mentioned, Intuitive is the maker of the da Vinci, a robotics system used for many minimally invasive procedures, from hernia repair to hysterectomy and gastric bypass surgeries, just to name a few.  The latest version, the da Vinci 5, has been used for more than 40 different procedure types so far.
